{"tid":1729700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打輿論戰] 五個月了，好心搞唔掂就妥協啦","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T13:22:25.000Z","uid":53853,"like":139,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f34f5e6885d3a5a7c499bd162ba9e7d01392d414","tid":1729700,"uid":53853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"老細係藍絲<br />\n當初佢支持政府強硬D 教下班細路<br />\n拎棍打，開槍射，總之唔好退讓<br />\n<br />\n不過近排生意差左好多<br />\n佢就開始噫噫哦哦，話咩五個月，越搞越亂<br />\n唔識搞就唔好搞，妥協應承班示威者啦 (當然，佢用既係曱甴)<br />\n<br />\n我問佢，林鄭話應承就法治會死<br />\n老細即刻怒屌，法治關我撚事呀，法治死我餓死先啦<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家可以執住呢個POINT去藍絲洗版<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識搞就唔會5個月都搞唔掂，搞唔掂就妥協，法治未死我餓死先啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8d444754a37340f85d933da99133e1c5cb50a1a","tid":1729700,"uid":53853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"和理非機會黎啦<br />\n打輿論戰呀快D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636e94008f88c2b959321eb8d69289e1a60eb306","tid":1729700,"uid":64981,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"【比警察睇既文宣】3萬警力都返唔到工，我要警察做乜？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1715926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1715926</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9FOD4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9FOD4r.jpg&h=fac19dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c428113dff5754b286792543d1d562736bcac2ef","tid":1729700,"uid":116054,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"藍絲：仆街，搞咁耐都搞唔掂，無撚用"},{"pid":"87e005f0e24ce134448a30a86b067c152f7f9613","tid":1729700,"uid":53853,"li